==Early Life==
Arthur Bispo Fernandes was born on August 4, 2012, in Olimpio Noronha, Brazil. He is a son of Matheus Rocha Fernandes (1988-2065), a paralegal, and mother Amanda Martins (1985-2076), a reporter.

When he was 4 years old (2016), Arthur broke his parents' lawnmower and then lied about it. When he was 5 years old (2017), Arthur told his mother that Blue is his favorite color.

==Primary School==
When he was 6 years old (2018), he started attending Martins Primary School. When he was 7 years old (2019), His mother gave birth to a brother named Enzo Fernandes. 11 months earlier when Arthur was 6 years old (2018), Enzo was concieved after they did sexual activities. When he was 11 years old (2023), his bichon frise, Daisy, died while finding a quiet place behind the house. Arthur almost diagnosed with depression after Daisy died. His mother gave birth to his brother, Anderson Fernandes, Arthur's new brother. He was a planned pregnancy. When he was 12 years old (2024), he got bullied at school by his classmate, Gabriel. He reported him to the headmaster's office a few minutes later. He later got attacked by him. When he was 13 years old (2025), His classmate, Pamela Matos (2012-), asked Arthur out to be his girlfriend. When he was 14 years old (2026), he was suffering from lice.

==Secondary School==
When he was 15 years old (2027), he finished primary school and started attending Chen Secondary School. He tried out for his secondary school wrestling team but did not make the cut. When he was 17 years old (2029), his girlfriend, Pamela, became pregnant with Arthur's baby. About a year later when he was 18 years old (2030), Pamela gave birth to a son named Lucas Fernandes. He had him circumcised 17 minutes later.

==University==
When he was 18 years old (2030), he graduated from secondary school and started attending university for free thanks to Brazil's public education system. Arthur started a university program in nursing. A few minutes later, a professional twerker and a cat lady hired him as a tutor. He earned $319 after working 29 hours for them at $11 an hour. When he was 19 years old (2031), Pamela became pregnant again with Arthur's baby. About a year later when he was 20 years old (2032), Pamela gave birth to a daughter named Maria-Clara Fernandes. Arthur also vaccinated Lucas Fernandes.

==Horse Jockey for Olimpio Noronha Downs==
