ffering a stroke. His little brother, Enzo Fernandes, and his wife, Joana, have adopted a 6-year-old girl named Manuela Conceicao. His daughter, Maria-Clara Fernandes, and her husband, Yuri, had a son named Ronaldo Castro. His son, Diogo, enlisted in the Air Force. His grandson, Matheus, has been diagnosed with whooping cough. When he was 54 years old (2066), his little brother, Anderson Fernandes, and Maria Luiza Nogueira divorced. When he was 55 years old (2067), he savored each moment as he enjoyed a naturally essenced and delightfully carbonated La Croix beverage. When he was 56 years old (2068), his grandson, Matheus, is no longer suffering from whooping cough. His mother was diagnosed with pneumonia. He earned $364 by promoting an extremely popular sports drink on his YouTube account. When he was 57 years old (2069), his mother is no longer suffering from pneumonia. He fully paid off the car loan on his brown Mercedes-Benz S-Class. He was forced to retire from his job as House Jockey for Olimpio Noronha Downs. He thanked his supervisor for the opportunity to serve Olimpio Noronha Downs.

