==Death==
Arthur Bispo Fernandes died in his sleep at the ripe old age of 89. His funeral was attended by his three loving children, Lucas, Maria-Clara, and Diogo, and seven of his eight grandchildren. His devoted wife, Pamela went to climb the neighbor's tree instead.

A charming fellow, he studied nursing in college. Arthur Bispo got a job as a horse jockey and was a faithful servant to Olimpio Noronha Downs, working there for 34 years. Friends say he liked circumcised penises.

He had 3 children, 8 grandchildren and 4 lovers.
